&lt;p&gt;    $ git pull &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/1ambda/kafka&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/1ambda/kafka&lt;/a&gt; &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/KAFKA-3742&quot; title=&quot;Can&amp;#39;t run connect-distributed.sh with -daemon flag&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;KAFKA-3742&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;KAFKA-3742&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;-connect-running-as-daemon&lt;/p&gt;

